title: How do I resolve error code 0x805A0194, shown in logs when the launching my Windows game?

sections.title: Symptoms
content: • I am receiving the error '0x805A0194' in my log when launching my Windows app.

sections.title: Cause
content: "UnityIAPWin8:Exception loading listing information:Exception from HRESULT: 0x805A0194" can be shown when the game's App ID is not known by Microsoft.

sections.title: Resolution
content: Check the following links for troubleshooting advice, or consider filing a support request with Microsoft:
